    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Bard, Cleric, or Druid)</i></div><p>This staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC and spellcasting ability modifier: <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.2Ll110Ua8S89zQgP]{cure wounds} (1 charge per spell level, up to 4th), <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.mLUmp8DbIVUcTgLc]{lesser restoration} (2 charges), or <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.Jk5U9E1RwcxwdRMp]{mass cure wounds} (5 charges).</p>\n<p>The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff vanishes in a flash of light, lost forever.</p>\n</div>",
